 - https://stackoverflow.com/questions/10420137/jaxb-xjc-mapping-to-existing-domain-objects
 - https://stackoverflow.com/questions/12891958/jax-b-how-to-map-a-schema-element-to-an-existing-java-class
 - https://stackoverflow.com/questions/23629801/jaxb-generates-listjaxbelement-instead-of-fields

[This Oracle article](https://docs.oracle.com/cd/E19316-01/819-3669/bnazf/index.html) is quite dated, but it provides a good explanation about how the actual correspondence between fields happens.

